===[[Pokémon Masters EX]]===
{{main|Jasmine (Masters)}}
Jasmine forms a [[sync pair]] with {{TP|Jasmine|Steelix}}, {{p|Celesteela}}, {{p|Ampharos}}, {{p|Magnemite}}, and {{p|Forretress}} in [[Pokémon Masters EX]]. Both her Steelix and Ampharos are capable of [[Mega Evolution|Mega Evolving]]. Jasmine became a playable sync pair on May 21, 2020.

Jasmine has also made notable appearances in one of the game's main stories, the [[villain arc]].

